+/*
+ * Macros for accessing the [V]PCLMULQDQ-based CRC functions that are
+ * instantiated by crc-pclmul-template.S
+ *
+ * Copyright 2024 Google LLC
+ *
+ * Author: Eric Biggers <ebiggers@google.com>
